108
00:06:53,041 --> 00:06:54,541
I do whatever I want,

109
00:06:54,625 --> 00:06:56,333
the world be damned,

110
00:06:56,416 --> 00:06:59,791
and if I don't do something,
then that's on me.

111
00:06:59,875 --> 00:07:02,291
