126
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,333
[KING OF DESPAIR]
I always win.

127
00:07:48,958 --> 00:07:51,083
What you guys don't know,

128
00:07:51,166 --> 00:07:54,250
is that all my pieces are
right where I want them.

129
00:07:54,333 --> 00:07:56,333
Well that was freakin' weird.

130
00:07:56,416 --> 00:07:58,125
What do you think that
light could have been?

131
00:07:58,208 --> 00:08:00,250
Which light d'ya mean?

132
00:08:00,333 --> 00:08:01,791
You didn't see it?

133
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:08,833
[crackling]

134
00:08:10,708 --> 00:08:12,958
[heart beating]

135
00:08:15,416 --> 00:08:18,500
