of the building into the sky.

136
00:08:18,583 --> 00:08:20,666
Like, well, kinda like that!

137
00:08:25,791 --> 00:08:27,875
--[horns honking]
--[crowd chattering]

138
00:08:27,958 --> 00:08:29,416
[ALIGURA]
Wow!

139
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:30,791
[KING OF DESPAIR]
Whoa, it worked?

140
00:08:30,875 --> 00:08:32,625
