the Shinatobe style.

181
00:10:30,041 --> 00:10:32,166
Gotta say, it's a nice
lookin' trident.

182
00:10:33,666 --> 00:10:34,791
[growls]

183
00:10:34,875 --> 00:10:35,791
Careful.

184
00:10:37,541 --> 00:10:39,583
[groans]

185
00:10:39,666 --> 00:10:42,041
[ZED] His lower half
is torn to shreds,

186
