us, you old floating dishrag!

201
00:12:00,250 --> 00:12:01,416
So ya wanna help?

202
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,791
I don't need an invitation!

203
00:12:03,875 --> 00:12:05,416
--[ZAPP] Kagutsuchi!
--[ZED] Shinatobe!

204
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:08,333
--[ZAPP] Seven Hells!
--[ZED] Heavenly Winged Bellows!

205
00:12:08,416 --> 00:12:09,833
[screeching]

206
00:12:16,458 --> 00:12:19,125
[KLAUS]
Herlelle Lucando Lozo.

207
00:12:19,208 --> 00:12:21,333
Thietkaua gi Murmhavat.

208
00:12:24,458 --> 00:12:27,125
I hereby seal you!

209
00:12:27,208 --> 00:12:28,916
[hissing]

210
00:12:30,916 --> 00:12:33,291
Brain Grid Blood
Battle Technique,

211
00:12:33,375 --> 00:12:35,250
form nine, nine, nine!

212
00:12:35,333 --> 00:12:38,333
Ewiges Gefangnis!

213
00:12:42,416 --> 00:12:44,250
Despise me.

214
00:12:44,333 --> 00:12:46,250
Forgive me.

215
00:12:46,333 --> 00:12:48,750
Resign yourself.

216
00:12:48,833 --> 00:12:51,125
I only commit
such brutality...

217
00:12:52,541 --> 00:12:55,708
to protect mankind!

218
00:13:00,875 --> 00:13:02,750
[JUGEI]
You've managed not to fail.

219
00:13:02,833 --> 00:13:05,500
Frankly, I'm amazed
you're not a pile of corpses,

220
00:13:05,583 --> 00:13:07,916
but you effectively
worked together by sensing

221
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,416
the other's abilities and
allowing them to perform

222
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:11,958
their necessary role.

223
00:13:12,041 --> 00:13:14,000
You're all barely worth
more than the paper

224
00:13:14,083 --> 00:13:15,791
